metadata.name: Ventura Highway
metadata.description:
Ventura highway in the sunshine  
Where the days are longer  
The nights are stronger  
Than moonshine  
You're gonna go I know

--

Throughout this collection I have used AI to create post-photography, making it a compelling representation of the intersection between past, present, and future. This artwork celebrates the idea of breaking free from conventions and societal norms and embarking on a journey toward an unknown but exciting future.

AI Generator: Midjourney  
Edition: 1/1  
Year: 2023  
Artist: Moonlight Media  
Dimensions: 2048x3072
